{"tid":1287081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"放棄自已既人真係好自私⋯","createTime":"2019-07-05T05:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T06:09:13.000Z","uid":272258,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f5d9b924919041f668be6e4e9e9b6fd757cbb7","tid":1287081,"uid":272258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:21:39.000Z","msg":"其實我真係對呢個行為好反感<br />\n你想放棄就叫我地行埋佢？<br />\n點解我地有2百萬人呀？<br />\n就係因為大家都喺度呀<br />\n你地死左我地仲邊度有2百萬人<br />\n可能你萬念俱灰 你覺得前路茫茫 死係唯一出路<br />\n但你出到來見到我地成班香港人齊心作戰 你好唔好意思dum低我地<br />\n就算你話你死你事條命你既 但而家香港人一條心 你死不單係你既事 仲係香港人既事 <strong>！！</strong><br />\n每多一個人死大家都多份傷感 唔識你都心痛咖大佬呀 唔好比呢個行為變成一種風氣呀 <br />\n如果你非常負面唔知點好 我相信除左防自殺會同社工外 你隨處開個post 隨街找個年輕人 大家都會花時間去開解你 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">真係唔好放棄你自己</span></span>"},{"pid":"24b81db64dc11d15e226ba9206caea2963642cd7","tid":1287081,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5581ff073f11f050f5e6fe0e5f96d9c29291d9d1","tid":1287081,"uid":200274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:29:02.000Z","msg":"香港母親？做老母做到你咁！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1287093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1287093</a>"},{"pid":"7ea710bfc4dc06fee7f82ba54a78ee7e72d50dcc","tid":1287081,"uid":272258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24b81db64dc11d15e226ba9206caea2963642cd7","tid":1287081,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"佢地離開我都難過 所以更唔想再有人去輕生"},{"pid":"7c1030eb111807623b6eb0ea8f7ff3b7ca693d9d","tid":1287081,"uid":272258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ea710bfc4dc06fee7f82ba54a78ee7e72d50dcc","tid":1287081,"uid":272258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24b81db64dc11d15e226ba9206caea2963642cd7","tid":1287081,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"佢地離開我都難過 所以更唔想再有人去輕生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:35:30.000Z","msg":"犧牲"},{"pid":"06ddd10ca47309d0080183a450def403c9958626","tid":1287081,"uid":268516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:45:14.000Z","msg":"輕生固然令人難過<br />\n<br />\n不過如果自己自殺要撚狗咁, 令同路人24小時全港十八區咁玩捉迷藏，自己就要諗吓，點解咁有勇氣去傷害+玩鳩一啲同你相同理念，著緊你，支持你嘅人，而放過啲真正玩鳩你嘅政權。<br />\n<br />\n有網台主持講過，有死嘅勇氣，就唔好浪費走去自殺<br />\n除非你驚做其他野<br />\n利申： 我無叫人犯法"},{"pid":"2148defb194aeb7e919f35587b29e2554167f13f","tid":1287081,"uid":18090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:02:30.000Z","msg":"其實樓主講得無錯<br />\n可以為香港做既野仲有好多<br />\n亦都需要大家既力量先完成到<br />\n多你一個就真係多一個<br />\n希望大家唔好再放棄自己！<br />\n真係要團結！<br />\n一起撐下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e7f8a3ad4013a42d55937fcd6879779560d19a","tid":1287081,"uid":175258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪做自私撚</span></span>"},{"pid":"d245b9bbe775f097d4a21cb47fe9a3dc1710ec7c","tid":1287081,"uid":143435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"放棄自己唔係自私，但我重想睇到準備放棄自己既人 唔放棄自己呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好離開我地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}